# String Calculator TDD Kata
Pure Ruby • RSpec • 100 % Green

## What you’re looking at
A zero-dependency Ruby service that solves the String Calculator TDD using Rspec.

- 8 examples  
- 8 commits (you can `git log --oneline` to check the commits)  
- Clean service-object architecture

## One-liner to run
```bash
bundle install && bundle exec rspec spec/services/string_calculator_spec.rb

# Project layout (Rails-convention)
- app/services/string_calculator.rb
- spec/services/string_calculator_spec.rb

